Product Description

For up to 3 x* the volume and a lightweight feel try Max Factor Xperience Volumising Mascara and let your lashes flutter. Your lashes look fuller thicker and more lifted* without the heavy or stiff feel some traditional mascaras can often leave behind. Make-up Artist Tips: For a fresh daytime look use Xperience Weightless foundation with a slick of Max Factor Xperience Volumising Mascara. Finish off with our sheer Xperience gloss balm. Need an emergency eye fix? Apply a quick coat of Xperience Volumising Mascara to the outer corners of your lashes and hide dark under eye circles with Masterpiece Mastertouch Concealer. Give your eyes a lift with two coats of Xperience Volumising Mascara and sharply define brows with Eyebrow Pencil in Hazel. Be sure to go in upward strokes for maximum effect. Big night out? For 30-second day to night eyes add a second coat of Xperience Volumising Mascara and a finger- smudged line of Kohl Pencil in Black. *vs bare lashes

Our longest brush ever reaches even the tricky corner lashes leaving you with corner to corner length and impact.
